" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Cryptogenic organizing pneumonia",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 340px; height: 271px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Forty-eight year old woman with an eight week history of cough, dyspnea with exertion, fatigue, and slight weight loss. Posteroanterior&nbsp;chest radiograph&nbsp;reveals bilateral volume loss with reticular opacities at both bases. There was improvement following&nbsp;glucocorticoid therapy, but the patient did not return to normal lung function or exercise capacity.",
